===[[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]===
{{main|Giovanni (Genetic Apex 223)}}
Giovanni makes an appearance as a {{TCG|Supporter}} card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]'s first expansion, {{TCGP|Genetic Apex}}. On the turn the player plays this card, attacks used by their Pokémon do an additional 10 damage to their opponent's Active Pokémon.

